    <h3 class="bg-primary text-white rounded p-2 text-center">About Us</h3>
    <p class="text-center mt-2">Welcome to Libooky, your go-to destination for a diverse collection of e-books available for purchase or borrowing. Our platform is designed to provide an easy and enjoyable reading experience for book lovers everywhere.</p>

    <h3 class="bg-primary text-white rounded p-2 text-center mt-4">Our Mission</h3>
    <p class="text-center mt-2">At Libooky, we believe that everyone should have access to a vast library of books without any barriers. Whether you're looking to buy the latest bestseller or borrow a classic novel, our mission is to bring the world of literature to your fingertips.</p>

    <h3 class="bg-primary text-white rounded p-2 text-center mt-4">What We Offer</h3>

