        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
            <h4 class="bg-warning text-white rounded p-2 text-center">Extensive Collection</h4>
            <p>We offer a wide range of e-books across various genres, including fiction, non-fiction, academic, self-help, and more. Our library is continuously updated to include the latest releases and timeless classics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
            <h4 class="bg-warning text-white rounded p-2 text-center">Flexible Options</h4>
